###Be Safe!

Since we're talking about dogs and cars, be sure to [never leave your pet](http://www.humanesociety.org/animals/resources/tips/help-dog-in-hot-car.html) in a hot vehicle.
Rolling down windows does not help much, a car can reach 100F in under 10 minutes if it is 80F outside.
Help keep your pup safe.


